---

<section class="py-24 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
            <div>
                <span
                    class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sage mb-4"
                    >The Breed</span
                >
                <h2
                    class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-forest mb-6 tracking-tight"
                >
                    Why Murray Grey Beef?
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
                    Not all beef is created equal. We chose Murray Greys for a
                    reason—they're the perfect breed for producing exceptional
                    grass-fed beef, and they're proudly Australian.
                </p>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-forest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-6 h-6 fill-mint-light"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L18 8l-9 9z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-forest text-lg mb-1">
                                Victorian Heritage Since 1905
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                                Developed right here in Victoria at Dooral,
                                Murray Greys are a true Australian success
                                story—bred to thrive on our pastures.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-forest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-6 h-6 fill-mint-light"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L18 8l-9 9z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-forest text-lg mb-1">
                                Natural Marbling on Grass
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                                Unlike many breeds that need grain to marble
                                well, Murray Greys develop beautiful
                                intramuscular fat on pasture alone—tender,
                                flavourful beef without the feedlot.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-forest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-6 h-6 fill-mint-light"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L18 8l-9 9z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-forest text-lg mb-1">
                                Calm Temperament, Better Beef
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                                Murray Greys are renowned for their docile
                                nature. Less stress throughout their lives means
                                lower cortisol and more tender, better-tasting
                                meat.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-forest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-6 h-6 fill-mint-light"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L18 8l-9 9z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-forest text-lg mb-1">
                                Ideal Frame for Quality Cuts
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                                Medium-framed with excellent fat coverage,
                                Murray Greys produce beef that's neither too
                                lean nor over-finished—just right for the
                                perfect eating experience.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative">
                <div
                    class="bg-linear-to-br from-forest/5 to-sage/10 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12"
                >
                    <div
                        class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-forest/5"
                    >
                        <div class="text-center mb-8">
                            <div
                                class="w-20 h-20 bg-linear-to-br from-warm to-warm-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="w-10 h-10 fill-white"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    ><path
                                        d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"
                                    ></path></svg
                                >
                            </div>
                            <h3
                                class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-forest mb-2"
                            >
                                Did You Know?
                            </h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
                            <p class="leading-relaxed">
                                Murray Greys were first bred in 1905 when a
                                black Shorthorn cow gave birth to a grey calf
                                after being mated with a Angus bull.
                            </p>
                            <p class="leading-relaxed">
                                That single calf founded an entire breed now
                                exported to over 30 countries—but they're still
                                proudly Victorian at heart.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-forest/10 flex items-center justify-center gap-4"
                        >
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div
                                    class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-forest"
                                >
                                    1905
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">
                                    Established
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-px h-12 bg-forest/10"></div>
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div
                                    class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-forest"
                                >
                                    30+
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">
                                    Countries
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-px h-12 bg-forest/10"></div>
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div
                                    class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-forest"
                                >
                                    VIC
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">
                                    Origin
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 bg-mint/20 rounded-full -z-10"
                >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
